## 🗓️ WEEKLY SPRINT PLAN (30–45 MIN / DAY)

> Sprint Length: **7 days**
> Goal: **Establish backend + API foundation**

### 🔹 Day 1 – Architecture & Setup (30–45 min)

* Decide backend stack (recommended below)
* Initialize backend repo
* Connect MongoDB

---

### 🔹 Day 2 – Auth Foundation

* Create user schema
* Add password hashing

---

### 🔹 Day 3 – Signup Flow

* Signup form → backend
* Store user data securely

---

### 🔹 Day 4 – Login + Remember Me

* Login endpoint
* Remember-me logic

---

### 🔹 Day 5 – Spoonacular API

* API service setup
* Fetch recipes successfully

---

### 🔹 Day 6 – Loading + Navigation

* Sync loading screen
* Navigate to recipe list when ready

---

### 🔹 Day 7 – Review & Cleanup

* Test flows end-to-end
* Fix bugs
* Plan next sprint

---

## 🛠️ BACKEND RECOMMENDATION (FOR YOU)

Given your stack and goals:

**Recommended:**

* Backend: **Node.js + Express**
* Database: **MongoDB (Atlas)**
* Auth: **JWT + bcrypt**
* Hosting (later): Render / Railway

This setup:

* Scales well
* Is React-friendly
* Is industry standard

